            alt="Photorealistic interior 3D Rendering of a modern house designed by Gregor Pils Architects. Contemporary interior design with wood and plaster. Building next to vineyards. Real Estate residential project. Still CG Image produced by Scuares, an architectural visualization studio"
          />
          <Credit author="Gregor Pils" project="Weinbergloft Houses" />
        </div>
        <div class="img-full">
          <img
