            alt="Photorealistic exterior 3D Rendering of a modern house designed by Gregor Pils Architects. Contemporary facade design with wood and plaster. Building next to vineyards. Real Estate residential project.  Still CG Image produced by Scuares, an architectural visualization studio"
          />
