            src="/images/pixel.jpg"
            data-src="williamsburg"
            width="1000"
            height="1211"
            style="aspect-ratio: 1000 / 1211"
            class="img-lazy"
            alt="Photorealistic exterior 3D Rendering of a modern co-living building in Williamsburg, New York. Architectural project designed by The Collective with a contemporary facade design made of brick. Real Estate project. Still CG Image produced by Scuares, an architectural visualization studio"
